                            The Best Laid Plans
                        </div>
                    

                    
                        <div id="breadcrumbs">
                            <a href="/groups-of-interest">Groups Of Interest</a> &raquo; <a href="/anderson-robotics-hub">Anderson Robotics Hub</a> &raquo; <a href="/end-of-line-hub">End of Line Hub</a> &raquo; The Best Laid Plans
